Key.Original: You notice vapors raising from the flask revealing beautiful blue crystals.
Key.English: You notice vapors raising from the flask revealing beautiful blue crystals.
Key.French: Vous remarquez,les vapeurs en s'échappant du ballon,que de magnifiques cristaux bleus apparaissent.
Key.Chinesesimp: 你注意到从烧瓶上升起的蒸汽并喷出美丽的蓝色晶体.

Key.Original: You accidentally nudge the flask enough to mess up the cooking process.
Key.English: You accidentally nudge the flask enough to mess up the cooking process.
Key.French: Vous mettez un petit coup dans le ballon.. juste assez pour rater la cuisson.
Key.Chinesesimp: 你不小心把瓶子推到了弄乱烹饪过程
Key.Chinese: 你不小心把瓶子推到了弄乱烹饪过程

Key.Original: Some dirt has gone into the flask and it's starting to produce smoke and flames.
Key.English: Some dirt has gone into the flask and it's starting to produce smoke and flames.
Key.French: De la poussuière est entré dans le ballon et commence à produire de la la fumée et des flammes.
Key.Chinesesimp: 一些污垢进入烧瓶，它开始产生烟雾和火焰
Key.Chinese: 一些污垢进入烧瓶，它开始产生烟雾和火焰

Key.Original: Applying heat doesn't start the chemical reaction and only burns the ingredients. Seems like an unlucky chemical error.
Key.English: Applying heat doesn't start the chemical reaction and only burns the ingredients. Seems like an unlucky chemical error.
Key.French: Chauffer ne fait pas réagir comme prévu et brule tous les ingrédients. Il semblerait que vous ayez fait une erreur.
Key.Chinesesimp: 施加热量不会引发化学反应，只会燃烧成分。 看起来像一个不幸的化学错误
Key.Chinese: 施加热量不会引发化学反应，只会燃烧成分。 看起来像一个不幸的化学错误

Key.Original: You managed to produce some green liquid like substance that is now about to catch fire. This is not definitely meth.
Key.English: You managed to produce some green liquid like substance that is now about to catch fire. This is not definitely meth.
Key.French: Vous commencez à produire une sorte de liquide vert, il faut maintenant chauffer. Ce n'est pas encore de la meth.
Key.Chinesesimp: 你设法产生一些即将着火的物质的绿色液体 确定这不是冰毒
Key.Chinese: 你设法产生一些即将着火的物质的绿色液体 确定这不是冰毒

Key.Original: Green smoke starts coming out of the cooking flask and some dark green slime is left in the flask. This is definitely not meth
Key.English: Green smoke starts coming out of the cooking flask and some dark green slime is left in the flask. This is definitely not meth
Key.French: De la fumée verte s'échappe du ballon et un dépot gluant vert sombre est précipité au fond. C'est pas du tout de la meth ça.
Key.Chinesesimp: 烟雾开始从烹饪瓶中冒出来，并且一些深绿色的粘液留在烧瓶中 确定这不是冰毒
Key.Chinese: 烟雾开始从烹饪瓶中冒出来，并且一些深绿色的粘液留在烧瓶中 确定这不是冰毒

Key.Original: You can notice flames and green smoke coming out of the cooking flask and some burned substance is left in the flask. This is definitely not meth.
Key.English: You can notice flames and green smoke coming out of the cooking flask and some burned substance is left in the flask. This is definitely not meth.
Key.French: Vous pouvez constater des flammes et de la fumée verte s'échappant du ballon de plus un précipité brulé réside au fond. C'est pas du tout de la meth ça.
Key.Chinesesimp: 您可以注意到从烹饪烧瓶中冒出的火焰和绿烟，烧瓶中留下了一些烧焦的物质 确定这不是冰毒
Key.Chinese: 您可以注意到从烹饪烧瓶中冒出的火焰和绿烟，烧瓶中留下了一些烧焦的物质 确定这不是冰毒

Key.Original: You can not reach this number right now.
Key.English: You can not reach this number right now.
Key.French: Vous ne pouvez pas contacter ce numéro pour l'instant
Key.Chinesesimp: 你现在不能联系这个号码
Key.Chinese: 你现在不能联系这个号码

Key.Original: Nothing selected. First search for the criminal, then select their name from the box and then click the button.

Key.Chinesesimp: 没有选择。 首先搜索罪犯，然后从框中选择他们的名字，然后点击按钮
Key.Chinese: 没有选择。 首先搜索罪犯，然后从框中选择他们的名字，然后点击按钮
